properties.areaDesc: Point Betsie to Sleeping Bear Point MI; Manistee to Point Betsie MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 18 at 12:43PM EST until January 19 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Highest gusts up to 40 kt and highest waves around 11
feet expected.

* WHERE...Point Betsie to Sleeping Bear Point MI and Manistee to
Point Betsie MI.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this afternoon to 7 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous highest waves which
could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 7 AM EST SUNDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IS CANCELLED
